            </p>
            <div class="platform-modes">
                <button class="mode-btn active" onclick="switchView('web')">🌐 Smartphone Ag-OS Engine View</button>
                <button class="mode-btn" onclick="switchView('sms')">💬 Offline SMS Fallback Gateway Node</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-layout">
            <div class="main-controls">
                
                <div id="web-panel" class="card">
                    <h2>Advanced AI Diagnostics & Predictive Research Lab</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 20px;">Persistent local session authenticated via cryptographic handshake validation.</p>
                    
                    <div class="avatar-container">
                        <div class="avatar-graphics">🤖</div>
                        <div>
                            <div style="color: var(--neon-green); font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;">APEX AI SYNCHRONIZER</div>
